sorcer.service.modeling

Interface Variability<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Arg, Call, Evaluation<T>, EvaluationComponent, Identifiable, Perturbation<T>, Request, Scopable, java.io.Serializable, Service, Setter, Substitutable, SupportComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Agent, Nsc, Proc, Srv, SysCall

    public interface Variability<T>
extends Identifiable, Evaluation<T>, Setter, Perturbation<T>, java.io.Serializable
    A variable has id, name and value. Its value can be evaluated by a related Evaluator.
